txt.en: 'In last night's fighting, many of our barricades were damaged or destroyed. If you wish to assist us, you could repair them so we will be ready for the next Ordâkhai assault.'
You have repaired the barricades protecting Sûru. You should return to Ningêna.
The barricades protecting Sûru from Ordâkhai attacks were damaged in recent fighting.
'The barricades are all repaired? Thank you [placeholder], you have been a great help.'
'If you wish to assist us, you could repair the barricades so we will be ready for the next assault.'
Ningêna has asked you to repair the barricades protecting Sûru.
